00:06:08,050 --> 00:06:11,560
Hey, did you see unit 404 come in?

75
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:14,370
No, I really didn't.

76
00:06:14,370 --> 00:06:17,360
Really, this bastard...

77
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:27,660
 What did this punk lock it with? The spare key won't even work.

78
00:06:31,620 --> 00:06:33,350
Wait a minute!

79
